Continuing with his hit-making wave, Nigerian music star, Kizz Daniel has released yet another potential hit song titled “Pah Poh”. The award-winning singer does not disappoint as his party fire-cracker is a raunchy afro-fusion number that has his impressive vocals, commendable delivery to delight listeners with a rocky attention-demanding hook. Pah Poh is mixed and mastered by renowned by Nigerian sound engineer, SWAPS while KrizBeatz produced the jam. Listen to the song below:  